# parallax ignore list — repos excluded from observation entirely, so they never
# enter belief or bias the priors. One glob per line (* = any non-slash run,
# ** = any, trailing / = dir and everything under). # comments allowed.
#
# Vendored upstream mirrors: huge behind-counts that are pure noise and would
# train the Beta prior toward "this repo moves constantly".
# e.g. a specific vendored fork:  some-org/vendored-upstream
**/vendor/**
**/node_modules/**
